(91, 179, 'GisÃ¨le / Claude Occelli', 'Nice, France', 'French', '<p data-start=\"70\" data-end=\"90\"><strong>GisÃ¨le Occelli</strong><br><strong>Representative â€“ France</strong></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"DepuisÂ 2009, nous avons dÃ©couvert de nombreux treks avec Mingmar SakeeÂ Sherpa. Nous l\'avons connuÂ la premiÃ¨re annÃ©e oÃ¹ il exerÃ§ait en tant que guide, pour une agence locale , puis en tantÂ que guide et organisateur. Nous avonsÂ toujours Ã©tÃ© satisfaits de ses prestations,Â  de sa rÃ©activitÃ© et de sa prÃ©venance.Â </div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nous souhaitons que son agence prospÃ¨re etÂ  qu\'il rÃ©alise vos projets de treks et expÃ©ditions en Himalaya\"</div>\r\n<p data-start=\"583\" data-end=\"643\">ğŸ“§E-mail : <a class=\"cursor-pointer\" rel=\"noopener\" data-start=\"593\" data-end=\"613\">gc.occelli@gmail.com</a><br data-start=\"613\" data-end=\"616\">ğŸ“ PhoneWhatsApp : +33 6 50 04 37 29</p>', '1753792605.jpg', 15, 'Nicolas', '1742982340543', 1, 0, '2025-03-26 09:45:40', '2025-12-15 18:50:20'),
(94, 173, 'Anne JARRY', 'Pratiquante bouddhiste et monitrice d\'Ã©quitation. Bretagne, France', NULL, '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pour dÃ©couvrir le NÃ©pal pour la premiÃ¨re fois, Lhakpa et Migmar m\'ont emmenÃ© dans des endroits fabuleux autour de Karmandu oÃ¹ je souhaitais rester.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Leur accompagnement m\'a complÃ¨tement sÃ©curisÃ©. Leur bonne humeur et leur professionnalisme sont remarquables, leur amour pour le NÃ©pal palpable et leur savoir de tous les us et coutumes absolument ouvert au partage.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ils m\'ont montrÃ© librement et joyeusement leur quotidien, me montrant les valeurs du NÃ©pal.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ce fut trÃ¨s inspirant pour moi.<br>J\'espÃ¨re et je souhaite revenir pour un voyage dans leur village dans les montagnes himalayennes.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Le NÃ©pal, c\'est gÃ©nial !</p>', '1747445307.jpg', 16, 'Anne-JARRY', '1747445307779', 1, 0, '2025-05-17 11:13:27', '2025-09-30 13:16:42'),
(95, 180, 'Phurwa Sherpa', 'Japan', 'Japanese English', '<p data-start=\"69\" data-end=\"113\"><strong data-start=\"69\" data-end=\"86\">Phurwa Sherpa</strong><br data-start=\"86\" data-end=\"89\"><strong>Representative â€“ Japan</strong></p>\r\n<p data-start=\"115\" data-end=\"364\">Born in the Solukhumbu District (Everest Region), I worked as a women trekking guide and led treks throughout Nepal. Over the years, I have had the pleasure of guiding travellers from many countries, including France, Japan, China, Canada, and more.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"366\" data-end=\"523\">I am currently living in Japan due to professional commitments, but I look forward to returning to Nepal and continuing my guiding work with Lhakpa Trekking.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"525\" data-end=\"712\">If you would like any information about travelling to Nepal, please feel free to reach out. Iâ€™d be delighted to share insights about my country and help you plan an unforgettable journey.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"714\" data-end=\"776\">ğŸ“§ Email: <a class=\"cursor-pointer\" rel=\"noopener\" data-start=\"724\" data-end=\"746\">japanlhatrek@gmail.com</a><br data-start=\"746\" data-end=\"749\">ğŸ“ Phone: +00</p>', '1753951220.jpg', 17, 'Phurwa-Sherpa', '1747446922607', 1, 0, '2025-05-17 11:40:22', '2025-12-15 18:55:16'),
(100, 173, 'Michele', 'voyageur | Experienced Global Guide', NULL, '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Michele is a globetrotter, passionate about travel and cultures, a lover of the voyage of discovery, the one that changes you every time.<br>He studied tourism in Italy, his country of birth, and has chosen Spain as his home for the last 20 years. He worked for 15 years as a tour guide, leading groups to discover the world, and has lived and worked in countless countries, some of which: Italy, England, Syria, Jordan, 6 years in Egypt, Mexico, Brazil, Thailand, Vietnam, Laos, Cambodia, Greece, and Cuba. He has also been on board cruise ships in the Caribbean but his real passion is backpacking. In 2015 he set off on a six-month trip to Asia, doing solidarity work in every country he touched, his final destination was in the country that has always attracted him for its impressive nature and its fantastic hospitable and smiling people: Nepal. Entering by bus from India in Kakarbhitta on an endless journey to Kathmandu, and when he meets up with Mingmar, sitting on his side, it is friendship at first sight! He falls in love with Nepal immediately and returns several times for trekking, with Mingmar\'s perfect, tailor-made planning, he works with 2 children\'s homes that soon become his chosen family and his everlasting link to this beautiful country. What strikes him most about Nepal is the absolute peace, the friendly people, the times to meditate and the incredible spaces where he can get lost and find himself again and again.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">ğŸ“§ <a class=\"cursor-pointer\" rel=\"noopener\" data-start=\"113\" data-end=\"136\">michelepiselli@yahoo.it</a></p>', '1753788902.jpg', 22, 'Michele-', '1753788902599', 1, 0, '2025-07-29 21:20:02', '2025-09-30 13:17:11'),
(101, 213, 'Michel', 'Italy  Spain', 'Italian Spanish', '<p data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"26\"><strong data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"26\">MicheleÂ <br>Representative Â Italy &amp; Spain</strong></p>\r\n<p data-start=\"28\" data-end=\"275\">I am an experienced globetrotter from Italy, passionate about travel and cultural discovery. After studying tourism, I spent 20 years in Spain and worked 15 years as a tour guide across countries like Egypt, Mexico, Brazil, and many more.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"277\" data-end=\"557\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">In 2015, a six-month solidarity journey brought me to Nepal, where I met Mingmar and formed an immediate friendship. Captivated by Nepalâ€™s peaceful nature and warm people, I have returned often for trekking and volunteer work with childrenâ€™s homes, making Nepal my second home.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"277\" data-end=\"557\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">Does anyone need some queries? Please, we are just for you and you can write in any language (English, Spanish, French).</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"277\" data-end=\"557\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">ğŸ“§Â <strong data-start=\"843\" data-end=\"853\">Email:</strong> michelepiselli@yahoo.it<br data-start=\"879\" data-end=\"882\">ğŸ“Â <strong data-start=\"885\" data-end=\"895\">Phone:</strong> +34669098906</p>', '1753789583.jpg', 23, 'Michele-', '1753789583741', 1, 1, '2025-07-29 21:31:23', '2025-12-15 18:56:44'),
