d)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Cold Weather Gear (For High-Altitude Regions)</strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\" type=\"square\">\r\n<li>Down jacket (800-fill recommended for subzero temperatures)</li>\r\n<li>Thermal gloves &amp; mittens</li>\r\n<li>Insulated trekking pants</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Rain Gear (Essential for Monsoon Season Treks)</strong></p>\r\n<ul type=\"square\">\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lightweight rain jacket (Gore-Tex or similar)</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Rain cover for backpack</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', 1, '2025-07-26 11:26:42', '2025-08-20 18:29:34'),
