le=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><hr align=\"center\" size=\"2\" width=\"100%\"></div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>7. Cancellation Policy</strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0in;\" type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l5 level1 lfo5; tab-stops: list .5in;\">More than 60 days before departure: full refund minus a â‚¬100 administrative fee.</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l5 level1 lfo5; tab-stops: list .5in;\">Between 30 and 59 days before departure: 50% refund of the total trip cost.</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l5 level1 lfo5; tab-stops: list .5in;\">Less than 30 days before departure: No refund.</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l5 level1 lfo5; tab-stops: list .5in;\">If the trip is cancelled by us due to safety concerns, political unrest, or adverse weather conditions, you will receive a full credit toward a future trip with us.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .5in;\">Â </p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>By Lhakpa Trekking:</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo8;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings; mso-fareast-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">Â§<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">Â  </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->If cancellation occurs due to unforeseen circumstances beyond our control (e.g., natural disasters, political instability), a full refund will be provided <strong>minus any unrecoverable costs</strong>, or the payment can be transferred to a future trip with Lhakpa Trekking.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo8;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings; mso-fareast-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">Â§<span st