nts beyond its control, such as weather, political unrest, or natural disasters.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>7. Changes &amp; Amendments</strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0in; list-style-type: square;\" type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l4 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list .5in;\">Lhakpa Trekking reserves the right to modify itineraries for safety or operational reasons.</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l4 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list .5in;\">Additional costs due to changes requested by the client are the clientâ€™s responsibility.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><hr align=\"center\" size=\"2\" width=\"100%\"></div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>8. Cancellation Policy</strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0in; list-style-type: square;\" type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l3 level1 lfo3; tab-stops: list .5in;\">More than 60 days before departure: full refund minus a â‚¬100 administrative fee.</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l3 level1 lfo3; tab-stops: list .5in;\">Between 30 and 59 days before departure: 50% refund of the total trip cost.</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l3 level1 lfo3; tab-stops: list .5in;\">Less than 30 days before departure: No refund.</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l3 level1 lfo3; tab-stops: list .5in;\">If the trip is cancelled by us due to safety concerns, political unrest, or adverse weather conditions, you will receive a full credit toward a future trip with us.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .5in;\">Â </p>\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><hr align=\"center\" size=\"2\" width=\"100%\"></div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>9. Liability &amp; Responsibility</strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0in; list-style-type: square;\" type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\