(76, NULL, 'Lower Everest', 'Witness the mixed culture and nature around Lower Everest Trekking routes to experience local lifestyle of Nepal which is almost as forgotten', 'triplist', 'lower-everest', '', '', 'The Pikey Peak Trek is the ideal choice if you want to go on a short, week-long walk to see Mount Everest in a less visited part of Nepal. This breathtaking hike leads us to the summit of Pikey Peak, which is 4065 meters above sea level. From there, we can see the magnificent Mt. Everest, Dhaulagiri, Numbur Himal, and numerous other nearby snow-capped Khumbu mountains. In the lower Everest region, this journey is regarded as the most rewarding. The Pikey Peak Trek also offers hikers a breathtaking experience as they pass through amazing paddy fields, natural waterfalls, thick forests, particularly rhododendron, sacred monasteries, and Sherpa traditional towns.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '10', '0', NULL, '2025-04-15 13:36:28', '2025-04-15 13:36:28'),
