(265, 242, 'Can I do this trek with under 8 year of child ?', 'Yes, you can do the Mardi Himal trek with a child under 8 years old, but it requires careful planning and precautions', 2, 1, '2025-05-27 12:55:31', '2025-08-11 14:41:16'),
(266, 242, 'Is it possible to do in 3 days ?', 'Yes, it is possible to do the Mardi Himal trek in three days, but only for very fit and experienced trekkers', 3, 1, '2025-05-27 12:55:31', '2025-12-21 16:00:44'),
(267, 242, 'Can I find lodges and teahouse everywhere ?', 'Yes, you can find lodges and teahouses throughout the Mardi Himal Trek, but the availability and comfort level vary by location', 4, 1, '2025-05-27 12:55:31', '2025-08-11 14:41:16'),
(268, 165, 'What should I prepare for this trip ?', 'You can basically prepare: Sun hat or Cap. You will be walking in the scorching sun for an average of 5-7 hours every day on the ABC trek, Knitted hat, Scarf or Neck Gaiter,  Base Layer, Waterproof and Windproof Shell,  Fleece Jacket, Hiking Pants and  Hiking Shorts.', 3, 1, '2025-05-27 15:14:18', '2025-12-21 15:56:37'),
(269, 165, 'Is it 1 or 2 itinerary ?', 'This is two itineraries but combined in one.', 4, 1, '2025-05-27 15:14:18', '2025-12-21 15:56:37'),
(270, 243, 'Why is it called Annapurna?', 'The name Annapurna comes from Sanskrit, where anna means \"food\" and purna means \"full\" or \"complete.\" Together, the name is often interpreted as \"provider of abundant food\" or \"eternal nourishment.\"', NULL, 1, '2025-05-27 19:52:19', '2025-05-27 19:52:19'),
